{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"首都少先队员给共青团十大的献诗","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1978,"month":10,"day":17}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"首都少先队员给共青团十大的献诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灿烂的阳光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照耀着我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宏伟的天安门广场；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月的金风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹拂着我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄严的人民大会堂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜艳的队旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬冬的队鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陪伴着我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共青团十大的会场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向敬爱的华主席致敬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向敬爱的党中央致敬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在这儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们怎能不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心潮汹涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热泪盈眶！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们共青团的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大哥哥大姐姐们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请你们听一听吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听一听少先队员的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衷心的祝贺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热切的希望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们可知道："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党中央的“五四通知”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样在我们心头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激起了一层层波浪？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们可知道："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们早也盼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚也盼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盼望这一天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把红领巾给你们献上？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天啊，今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们怎能不想起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那毕生难忘的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福时光——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们怎能不想起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席谆谆教导："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好好学习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天向上；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席戴上红领巾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高兴地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在我们中间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑声朗朗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们怎能不想起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周总理来到少年宫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同我们一起游戏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起照像，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲切鼓励我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快成长！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们怎能不想起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱委员长参加游园会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人家高兴地和我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么和蔼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么慈祥！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们怎能不想起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们成长的路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有多少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老一辈革命家的心血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洒满了党的雨露阳光！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，亲爱的祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的革命长辈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的共青团"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——我们的兄长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给了我们知识，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给了我们理想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给了我们幸福，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给了我们力量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从不懂事的娃娃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成为党的幼儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早晨八九点钟的太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天啊，今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来到庄严雄伟的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民大会堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又怎能抑制住"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满腔怒火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愤怒地控诉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万恶的林彪、“四人帮”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们举着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罪恶的砍刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摧残了少先队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扼杀了共青团，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直指向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们伟大的党！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关闭了少年宫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"停办了少年报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧毁了儿童读物，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砸碎了教室的门窗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"取消了我们的队名，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"践踏了我们的队旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让星星火炬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暗然无光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么交白卷的“英雄”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来是汪汪狂吠的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条疯狗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么反师道尊严，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不过是挑拨师生关系"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的阴谋勾当！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们鼓吹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闹而优则仕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们煽动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打砸抢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴巴上花言巧语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比蜂蜜还要甜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实际上是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毒害青少年一代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成为“文盲”加“流氓”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沧海横流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方显出英雄本色；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豺狼当道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锻炼了斗争闯将！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的大哥哥大姐姐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们看到了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们冲锋陷阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象海燕迎着风暴翱翔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真不愧为我们的榜样！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那难忘的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九七六年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万青年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾带领着我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉痛悼念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬爱的周总理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愤怒声讨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"残暴的“四人帮”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们看到了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"首都人民英雄纪念碑前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英勇搏斗的韩志雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚强不屈的贺延光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，雨花台下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反动的禁令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禁不住李西宁；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑牢房中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"法西斯死刑的威胁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吓不倒窦守芳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕林彪的鹰犬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕“四人帮”的棍棒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忠贞不屈，意志如钢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是社会主义时代的刘胡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是七十年代的黄继光！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们也看到了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鞍山的王素慧姐姐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇挑重担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜战斗在铁矿；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全能焊手张荣富哥哥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的名字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟电焊一样闪光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖南的喻应勇哥哥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七个春节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在夺煤战斗中度过；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江西的钟志民哥哥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扎根农村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让老根据地山河变样；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年数学家张广厚哥哥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刻苦攻关，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为国争光……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们按照"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席、党中央的号令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨上千里骏马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔驰在新长征路上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了四个现代化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤奋劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刻苦钻研，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了建设社会主义强国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你追我赶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大干快上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千千万万"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年英雄啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为我们少先队员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树立了杰出的榜样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满园香花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能辨得出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪一朵最芬芳？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满天星斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能认得清"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪一颗最明亮？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天啊，今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国山河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"繁华似锦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里征途，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铺满金光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们少先队员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能抑制住"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心头的激荡！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十年前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的“小五年计划”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为伟大的毛泽东时代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"增添了一份春光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天啊，今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在华主席领导下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要为四个现代化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贡献出一份力量！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在雷锋叔叔的塑像下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万个雷锋在成长；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在刘文学牺牲的土地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又出现了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少年英雄何运刚……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少少先队员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下定决心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向科学难关进军；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的小伙伴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戴着红领巾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进大学的课堂……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万丈高峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要去攀越；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千斤重担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们敢来承当。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天的红领巾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天的红旗手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天的少先队员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天的突击队猛将。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的党啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你哺育我们长大成人；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的共青团啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你带领我们奔向前方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要让祖国的现代化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提前完成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的伟大旗帜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永放光芒！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党旗啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在前面引路；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团旗啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在迎风飘扬；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的队旗啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧紧跟上！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路东风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路战鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路阳光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的大军永远向前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就象那奔腾的黄河长江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着四个现代化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着共产主义远方！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"name":"四人帮","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}